# AGENTS.md
# Python Preferred Rule — Canonical Version
# All other agent dirs reference or mirror this file.
# Reference: .kilocode/PYTHON_PREFERRED.md (full version)

## Mandate

All new automation scripts MUST use Python (.py).
Python 3.10+ required (type hints support).

## Exceptions

- npm scripts in package.json (Node.js ecosystem)
- CI/CD workflows (GitHub Actions YAML)
- Git hooks (pre-commit)
- One-liners in documentation

## Required Libraries

- `paramiko` — SSH client functionality
- `psutil` — System monitoring
- `subprocess` (stdlib) — Shell command execution

## Migration Status

- [x] collect-evidence.sh → collect_evidence.py
- [x] safe-ssh.sh → safe_ssh.py
- [x] debug-network.sh → debug_network.py

## Scripts Location

`.kilocode/scripts/server-monitor/` — Python server monitoring scripts

